1.4.0
=====

2024-02-03

Modernize and improve:

* Convert injected shell variables to regular awk variables.
* Add DEBUG flag and improve debugging aids.
* Move cached menu from /tmp to $XDG_RUNTIME_DIR.
* Improve reading translations.
* Update copyright notice.
* Allow setting icon size in ~/.gmenu2rc.
* Bump version to 1.4.0.
* Update README.

1.3.0
=====

2019-09-11

* Undepend on gmenu-fdcp control panel extension (Fatdog64 > 802).
* New packaging.
* Add README and manual page.
* (i18n) Change TEXTDOMAIN.
* Fix desktop file category.
* Fix missing control panel submenu keyboard accelerators.

1.2.0
=====

2017-03-03

* Added automatic menu label mnemonics. Dependency: gtkmenuplus 1.1.5.
* Fixed some issues.

1.0.1
=====

2017-01-06

* Show Fatdog64 Control Panel as a submenu. Dependency: gmenu2-fdcp.

1.0.0
=====

2016-09-19

* First release.

